01:10:04,800 --> 01:10:05,994
Okay.

1128
01:10:07,703 --> 01:10:10,171
- What do they want?
<i>- You're not going to like it.</i>

1129
01:10:10,306 --> 01:10:11,967
What?! What is it?

1130
01:10:12,541 --> 01:10:15,237
<i>They want at least one</i>
<i>hostage released and...</i>

1131
01:10:15,611 --> 01:10:17,340
And what?

1132
01:10:18,814 --> 01:10:21,374
<i>One of you has to turn yourself in.</i>

1133
01:10:30,125 --> 01:10:32,753
Fine. They can have Jessica.

1134
01:10:33,362 --> 01:10:36,229
Really?
You'd turn her in? Just like that?

1135
01:10:36,398 --> 01:10:39,185
<i>What do I care? You want out</i>
<i>and I want in.</i>

1136
01:10:39,201 --> 01:10:40,919
<i>Take Jessica as your insurance...</i>

1137
01:10:40,936 --> 01:10:43,632
<i>and the cops get their</i>
<i>precious negotiation pawn.</i>

1138
01:10:47,142 --> 01:10:48,837
Sounds like a plan.

1139
01:10:56,151 --> 01:10:58,676
What's wrong?
This is our way out.

1140
01:11:11,700 --> 01:11:15,966
That might be the sweetest thing
anyone has ever done for me.

1141
01:11:18,540 --> 01:11:19,632
Really?

1142
01:11:36,825 --> 01:11:38,793
Right. Let's get
the hell out of here.

1143
01:11:52,474 --> 01:11:53,429
What are you doing?

1144
01:11:53,442 --> 01:11:56,161
I'm setting up our next rendezvous
outside this vault.

1145
01:11:56,178 --> 01:11:58,669
Really? Is that a second date?

1146
01:12:01,216 --> 01:12:02,774
You'd better tie me up.

1147
01:12:05,187 --> 01:12:08,213
So Simon still thinks
I'm still your hostage.

1148
01:12:08,957 --> 01:12:10,754
You wish.

1149
01:12:11,994 --> 01:12:13,723
You want to help me with this?

1150
01:12:18,033 --> 01:12:19,523
Is this good?

1151
01:12:19,935 --> 01:12:21,163
That's good.

1152
01:12:59,808 --> 01:13:01,708
<i>All right, I'm coming out.</i>

1153
01:13:03,846 --> 01:13:05,677
I don't want any trouble!

1154
01:13:24,066 --> 01:13:25,818
I imagined you taller.

1155
01:13:25,834 --> 01:13:30,669
Fuck me, Jinx. Nice Attitude!
You've come a long way today.

1156
01:13:49,358 --> 01:13:51,087
I can't go out there like this.

1157
01:13:51,293 --> 01:13:53,761
I'm supposed to be a hostage
like you, not your hostage.

1158
01:13:56,265 --> 01:13:58,062
They're gonna know something is up.

1159
01:14:03,539 --> 01:14:05,564
You're supposed to be my hostage
for Simon's sake...

1160
01:14:05,574 --> 01:14:07,405
if we want to get away with this.

1161
01:14:10,145 --> 01:14:12,045
What do you suggest we do?

1162
01:14:18,153 --> 01:14:20,348
Be careful that thing's loaded.

1163
01:14:20,589 --> 01:14:21,510
Shit.

1164
01:14:21,523 --> 01:14:23,491
Wait one fucking minute you two!

1165
01:14:50,819 --> 01:14:52,844
Go, come on.

1166
01:14:59,127 --> 01:15:00,651
Put your gun down!

1167
01:15:00,796 --> 01:15:03,629
Put that gun down, motherfucker!

1168
01:15:05,033 --> 01:15:06,660
Move.

1169
01:15:14,276 --> 01:15:15,766
Move, motherfucker!

1170
01:15:17,679 --> 01:15:19,112
Do you understand me?

1171
01:15:23,252 --> 01:15:25,277
You have the right to remain silent.

1172
01:15:25,287 --> 01:15:27,938
If you cannot afford an attorney,
one will be appointed for you.

1173
01:15:27,956 --> 01:15:33,053
Do you understand the rights
I have just stated.

1174
01:15:33,161 --> 01:15:35,959
Out of the way, come on.

1175
01:15:36,298 --> 01:15:38,232
Got it.

1176
01:15:40,969 --> 01:15:42,197
<i>Oh can you hear me?</i>

1177
01:15:42,471 --> 01:15:43,392
<i>Damn. How about now?</i>

1178
01:15:44,773 --> 01:15:46,707
<i>Yes, loud and clear.</i>

1179
01:15:47,342 --> 01:15:50,140
<i>Good, okay, where were we?</i>
<i>Chump change.</i>

1180
01:15:50,812 --> 01:15:53,372
<i>The dime you don't even</i>
<i>bother picking up is...</i>

1181
01:15:53,382 --> 01:15:56,169
<i>the same dime we</i>
<i>all get bent- over for.</i>

1182
01:15:56,184 --> 01:15:59,950
<i>So, surcharge the surchargers!</i>
<i>I agree.</i>

1183
01:16:00,656 --> 01:16:02,954
<i>But there is one flaw</i>
<i>in your plan.</i>

1184
01:16:03,125 --> 01:16:05,525
Oh, a flaw in my plan?

1185
01:16:06,662 --> 01:16:09,017
<i>If we've got the PIN</i>
<i>and you've got the accounts...</i>

1186
01:16:09,031 --> 01:16:12,125
<i>what happens next?</i>
<i>What happens when we meet?</i>

1187
01:16:12,134 --> 01:16:14,102
<i>Trust the fatal flaw.</i>

1188
01:16:15,804 --> 01:16:17,431
<i>Well, there's only one answer.</i>

1189
01:16:19,474 --> 01:16:23,638
<i>Did you know that statistics say</i>
<i>that 98% of all convicted criminals...</i>

1190
01:16:23,645 --> 01:16:26,136
<i>have successfully committed</i>
<i>at least one previous crime...</i>

1191
01:16:26,148 --> 01:16:28,241
<i>before they were caught?</i>

1192
01:16:29,351 --> 01:16:32,980
<i>That means almost everyone gets</i>
<i>away with it at least once!</i>

1193
01:16:33,255 --> 01:16:37,248
<i>They had a good thing. But no,</i>
<i>they had to go try their luck again.</i>

1194
01:16:38,694 --> 01:16:41,151
<i>Oh. By the way, tip 10...</i>

1195
01:16:43,231 --> 01:16:45,324
<i>Know when to walk away.</i>

